        <item>
            <title>Meta 放弃与 Apple Vision Pro 竞争，转移重心开发低成本 VR 装置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:30:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[La Jolla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Meta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vr]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258883</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">根据 The Information 的报道，Meta 正计划取消开发与 Apple Vision Pro 直接竞争的高阶头戴式 VR 装置，由于其代号为 La Jolla 的高阶头戴式 VR 装置所需的 Micro OLED 屏幕成本过于高昂，未来将转移重心至开发低成本的 VR 装置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1258902 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/applevisionprovsmeta-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/applevisionprovsmeta-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/applevisionprovsmeta.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.roadtovr.com/meta-quest-3-apple-vision-pro-resolution-resolving-power-display-quality/">Road to VR</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Meta 原本的计划是将高阶头戴式 VR 装置 La Jolla 于 2027 年推出并与 Apple 的 Vision Pro 直接竞争，并将其定价于 1000 美元以下。消息指出 La Jolla 为了使用与 Vision Pro 相同的显示技术而采用了更昂贵的 Micro OLED 屏幕，但成本实在太高而正式取消开发高阶头戴式 VR 装置的计划。Meta 的首席技术总监 Andrew Bosworth 亦在 Threads 上暗示了这个决定，他表示一直在研究多个原型机，但不是每一个都会投入生产，某些项目被放弃的情况经常会出现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1258886 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meta-694x318.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="318" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meta-694x318.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/meta.jpg 1222w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.threads.net/@boztank/post/C_BS8BuPfQZ">Threads @boztank</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Meta 之前推出的高阶头戴式 VR 装置 Quest Pro 未有得到市场强烈的回响，其虽然以「高阶」产品作推广，但仍然使用低阶的 LCD 屏幕。虽暂不打算继续开发高阶市场，Meta 仍然会全力开发低阶至中阶的头戴式 VR 装置，其中包括预计会在 2026 年推出的 Quest 4，而 9 月将有机会推出 Quest 3 的新版本作为加入 Meta 生态系统的入门装置，价格约为 300-400 美元并有机会将其命名为 Quest 3S。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.flatpanelshd.com/news.php?subaction=showfull&amp;id=1724655513&amp;fbclid=IwY2xjawE6gDxleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHSM0fO-BQxwWbEWMRGsTYvyJ6_DGIACYhEzPe4McYbIkLl51XDbKtMdUNw_aem_PI5M2mufbGuMGGDe-HpkXA">FlatpanelsHD</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://appleinsider.com/inside/apple-vision-pro/vs/apple-vision-pro-vs-meta-quest-heatsets---how-the-approaches-compare">AppleInsider</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/apple-vision-pro-preorder-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】Apple Vision Pro 香港预订教学　戴眼镜也能轻松买 + 脸部扫描过程</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/26/taobao-xiaomi-vision-pro-trial-su7-car/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">安坐家中 Vision Pro 云端试车　淘宝小米合作推虚拟小米 SU7 试车体验</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/21/aic-warns-hkgov/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Google、Amazon、Meta 向香港发出警告，忧基建电脑安全立法影响网络供应商诚信</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/">Meta 放弃与 Apple Vision Pro 竞争，转移重心开发低成本 VR 装置</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/meta-cancelled-lajolla-fro-low-budget-vr/vr-mr-ar/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>全新 Porsche 电动 Macan 香港预览   800V 架构快速充电 + 可配气压避震及后轮转向</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/porsche-macanev-800v/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=porsche-macanev-800v</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/porsche-macanev-800v/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Macan 4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Macan Turbo EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Porsche Macan Electric]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258790</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新 Porsche Macan Electric 纯电动 SUV 最近正式于湾仔保时捷旗舰店进行闭门预览，场中展出了包括 Macan 4 及 Macan Turbo 两款全新电动 SUV，预计厂方将于 10 月正式推出，最快可于今年第四季交付。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258853" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112722-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112722-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112722.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112757-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112757-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112757.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Macan Turbo EV</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112942-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112942-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112942.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113121-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113121-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113121.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Macan 4</p><p>场中展出的两款新车均属香港规格的右軚版本，新车采用了全新的 Porsche PPE（Premium Platform Electric）800V 充电架构，当使用 800V 充电站时 DC 直流快充效率可高达 270kW，并于 21 分钟将电池电量由 10% 充至 80%。两款新车型号均配备 100kWh 锂电池，前后双马达组成的 4WD 系统， Macan 4 标准版马力为 408 匹、650Nm 扭力，0-100km/h 加速为 5.2 秒，续航力为 613 公里 (WLTP)。而高级版 Macan Turbo 马力达 639 匹，最高扭力为 1,130Nm，0-100km/h 加速只需 3.3 秒，续航力为 591 公里 (WLTP)。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258869" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113210-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113210-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113210.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112710-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112710-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112710.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_1125430-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_1125430-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_1125430.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112902-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112902-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/up