ontent/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112916-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112916-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112916.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Macan Turbo EV</p><p>全新 Macan EV 采用了分离式 LED 矩阵式头灯，车窗亦采用线条更简洁利落的无边框车窗，全新主动式空气力学套件 (PAA) 及新设计的扰流装置令 Macan EV 风阻系数只有 0.25Cd。内笼方面，新车采用 12.6 吋悬浮式曲面数码化表板，整合通讯功能的 10.9 吋中央萤幕及可选配的 10.9 吋乘客萤幕及 HUD 投射功能。新车暂定售价为: Macan 4 ($1,048,000) / Macan Turbo ($1,448,000)。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112455-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112455-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112455.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112405-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112405-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_112405.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113139-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113139-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240827_113139.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258878